prompt:
You are preparing a Detailed Project Report (DPR) for bank loan purposes.

Generate the section exactly in the following structure and format:

Title:
"1. Constitution of the Firm"

First write one short paragraph describing the firm and ownership.

Then provide bullet points exactly in this format with label, colon, and value:

• Firm Name            : {{firm_name}}
• Type of Organisation : {{organisation_type}}
• Proprietor Name      : {{proprietor_name}}
• PAN No.              : {{pan_number}}
• Aadhar No.           : {{aadhar_number}}
• Caste                : {{caste}}
• Residential Address  : {{residential_address}}

Rules:
- Use only the above structure.
- Maintain exact labels and spacing before colon.
- Do not add extra headings, tables, or explanations.
- Language must be formal and suitable for bank DPR.
